《'''你一生的故事'''》（{{lang-en|''Story of Your Life''}}）是[[姜峯楠|姜峯楠]]創作的[[科幻|科幻]][[中篇小說|中篇小說]]。本書的主題是以[[決定論|決定論]]、[[語言|語言]]和[[薩丕爾-沃爾夫假說|薩丕爾-沃爾夫假說]]來探索故事。

小說獲得2000年{{link-en|星雲獎最佳中篇小說|Nebula Award for Best Novella}}，還有1999年{{link-en|史鐸金獎|Theodore Sturgeon Award}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://nebulas.sfwa.org/nominated-work/story-of-your-life/ |title = "Story of Your Life" by Ted Chiang, Winner, Best Novella in 1999 |publisher = nebulas.sfwa.org |language = en |accessdate = 2017-01-16 |archive-date = 2019-05-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190515075746/https://nebulas.sfwa.org/nominated-work/story-of-your-life/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

本作被改編成2016年電影《[[異星入境|異星入境]]》。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.tor.com/2016/08/08/first-look-arrival-amy-adams-jeremy-renner-ted-chiang/ |title = Your First Look at Arrival, the Adaptation of Ted Chiang’s Novella Story of Your Life |author = Natalie Zutter |date = 2016-08-08 |publisher = Tor.com |language = en |accessdate = 2017-01-16 |archive-date = 2019-07-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190728080601/https://www.tor.com/2016/08/08/first-look-arrival-amy-adams-jeremy-renner-ted-chiang/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 梗概 ==
语言学家路易斯·班克斯和理论物理学家伊恩·唐纳德利受军方之命研究外星生物“七肢桶”的语言。

